### ===== CATEGORY MANAGEMENT =====

### 1. CREATE Category
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bộ vi xử lý",
  "description": "CPU và Processor"
}

### 2. GET All Categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories

### 3. GET Category by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1

### 4. GET Category by Name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories/search/Bộ%20vi%20xử%20lý

### 5. UPDATE Category
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bộ vi xử lý (Updated)",
  "description": "CPU và Processor - Updated"
}

### 6. DELETE Category
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1

### ===== PRODUCT MANAGEMENT =====

### 7. CREATE Product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Intel Core i7",
  "sku": "CPU001",
  "description": "Bộ xử lý Intel thế hệ 13",
  "price": 15000000,
  "category": {"id": 1}
}

### 8. GET All Products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### 9. GET Product by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### 10. GET Product by SKU
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/sku/CPU001

### 11. GET Products by Category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/category/1

### 12. UPDATE Product
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Intel Core i9",
  "sku": "CPU001",
  "description": "Bộ xử lý Intel thế hệ 13 - Updated",
  "price": 20000000,
  "category": {"id": 1}
}

### 13. DELETE Product
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### ===== INVENTORY MANAGEMENT =====

### 14. CREATE Inventory
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": {"id": 1},
  "quantity": 50,
  "minQuantity": 10,
  "warehouse": "Kho 1 - Hà Nội"
}

### 15. GET All Inventory
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory

### 16. GET Inventory by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/1

### 17. GET Inventory by Product ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/product/1

### 18. GET Inventory by Warehouse
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/warehouse/Kho%201%20-%20Hà%20Nội

### 19. UPDATE Inventory
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": {"id": 1},
  "quantity": 100,
  "minQuantity": 15,
  "warehouse": "Kho 2 - TP HCM"
}

### 20. UPDATE Inventory Quantity Only
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/1/quantity?quantity=75

### 21. CHECK Low Stock
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/1/low-stock

### 22. DELETE Inventory
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/1

